{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"146874-rumah-malar-yang-besar","title":"Rumah Malar Yang Besar","description":"Malar suka membina. Apa yang akan dia bina hari ini?","language":"Malay","langCode":"ms","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Lydia Aderus"],"illustrators":["Ankitha Kini"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Jala","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/146874-rumah-malar-yang-besar"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/715434/size3/5613393324b2c4300bc530bb88cb1e16.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/715434/size6/5613393324b2c4300bc530bb88cb1e16.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101106/size6/00f790a6005d8d79316f20c352de0ade.jpg","text":"Hari ini, Malar akan membina sebuah rumah besar!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101264/size6/3fd8eb8bc51f989ba470a5ddc77e567b.jpg","text":"“Saya boleh pakai semua ini!”","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101259/size6/41dff234905b14d6cf11f3b2d98b1422.jpg","text":"“Rumah besar saya akan menjadi setinggi ini!” kata Malar.\n“Dan seluas ini!”","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101109/size6/605f471213cd148167931d98d9991cf6.jpg","text":"Malar menyusun gelas atas satu sama lain","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101110/size6/8b0a514aec01a0033199503d6d247ebe.jpg","text":"Semua gelas-gelas itu jatuh ke bawah.\nTung! Tang! Dhadoom!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101111/size6/adbd9138c42c15c14fbd876001e71c00.jpg","text":"Malar mengambil gelas-gelas dan mencuba lagi.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101112/size6/a980a64397d162bce33ae2c4bea0218c.jpg","text":"Tung!\nDhadoom!\nTang!\nMereka jatuh. Sekali lagi!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101113/size6/9a2d994b9b890adfec95cfb3422237d7.jpg","text":"Kali ini, gelas tidak jatuh. Semakin tinggilah, mereka menjadi!\nMalar berfikir panjang.\nDia mencuba sekali lagi.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101114/size6/a3e41dac446486caa4e48ce5dd4145b4.jpg","text":"Rumah Malar yang besar dan berkilat\nhampir siap.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101206/size6/9a4c8370d86c40f1e76ce461ab374d52.jpg","text":"Malar bergegas ke dapur. Semua orang sibuk.\n“Apakah yang awak perlukan, Malar?” tanya Ayah.\n“Bolehkah awak bagi saya setengah daripada kelapa itu, Ayah? Rumah saya memerlukan bumbung.”\n“Ah ya! Betul itu,” kata Ayah.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101117/size6/bdc9e3323c1892e0604c021696acea17.jpg","text":"“Adakah awak suka rumah besar saya, Ayah?”\n“Ya, saya suka. Ini adalah sebuah istana yang indah!”","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101262/size6/66f946940a701eaad74f174a6ffb6a94.jpg","text":"DABADABA-DUM! TUNG! TANG!\nApakah yang akan Malar bina seterusnya?","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101119/size6/549f49fa0f483bba8d669a28422c8f5a.jpg","text":"Binalah Istana Anda Sendiri\nAnda perlukan:\n- Seberapa banyak cawan kertas yang anda boleh dapatkan\n- 1 bekas bulat dari dapur anda\n- Krayon atau pensel warna\n- 1 kelapa (dipotong separuh)\nTa-da! Istana anda sudah siap!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":13,"words":173}}